Package oracle.kubernetes.operator.watcher

Class Watcher<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.kubernetes.operator.watcher.Watcher<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the object to be watched.

    public class Watcher<T>
extends Object
    This class handles the Watching interface and drives the watch support for a specific type of object. It runs in a separate thread to drive watching asynchronously to the main thread.
